trans-unit.target: 表示 Ws-trust 参与者元素。

trans-unit.source: The wst:Participants element is an extension to the wst:RequestSecurityToken element and is used to pass information about which parties are authorized to participate in the use of the token.
trans-unit.target: Wst:Participants 元素是 wst: requestsecuritytoken 元素的扩展，用于传递有关哪些方有权参与使用令牌的信息。

trans-unit.source: For more information about the element that this class represents, see the version of the WS-Trust specification that applies to your scenario.
trans-unit.target: 有关此类表示的元素的详细信息，请参阅适用于你的方案的 Ws-trust 规范的版本。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.Participants"></xref> class.
Gets the list of participants that are allowed to use the token.
trans-unit.target: 获取允许以使用该令牌的参与者的列表。

trans-unit.source: Each item in the list contains the contents of a wst:Participant element.
trans-unit.target: 在列表中的每个项都包含 wst:Participant 元素的内容。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the primary user of the issued token.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置已颁发令牌的主要用户。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.ServiceModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference> that contains the address of the primary user of the token.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference>包含令牌的主要用户的地址。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference>

trans-unit.source: This is the contents of the wst:Primary element.
trans-unit.target: 这是 wst:Primary 元素的内容。
